Susan?

36:18.609 --> 36:23.380
[phone ringing]

36:23.382 --> 36:26.950
(ellie)
yeah.

36:28.619 --> 36:31.821
Thanks for stopping by,
ms. Wright.

36:31.823 --> 36:33.557
We did a little
digging on you.

36:33.559 --> 36:35.125
So what?

36:35.127 --> 36:38.795
About your husband
and your children

36:38.797 --> 36:40.397
And what everyone
said about you

36:40.399 --> 36:41.831
But could never prove.

36:41.833 --> 36:43.633
What do you want
from me?

36:43.635 --> 36:45.001
You threatened me.

36:45.003 --> 36:46.303
I want you to know
that I'm the one

36:46.305 --> 36:48.338
Who tipped off
the police,

36:48.340 --> 36:50.040
In case you were
wondering.

36:50.042 --> 36:51.708
Isn't that right,
detectives?

36:54.912 --> 36:57.147
Hey, boy.

36:57.149 --> 36:59.182
You remember me,
right?

36:59.184 --> 37:02.219
She left you out here
all alone, huh?

37:02.221 --> 37:03.386
That's no good.

37:03.388 --> 37:04.888
We can't have that.
Come on.

37:04.890 --> 37:05.989
(emmett)
if you cannot afford
an attorney,

37:05.991 --> 37:07.891
One will be provided
for you.

37:07.893 --> 37:09.259
<i>Where's my dog?</i>
<i>Do you understand</i>
<i>the rights</i>

37:09.261 --> 37:10.260
<i>I've just read to you?</i>
<i>Archie!</i>

37:10.262 --> 37:12.028
Archie!

37:12.030 --> 37:15.599
[shouting]
who took my dog?

37:23.341 --> 37:26.409
[phone ringing]

37:27.712 --> 37:29.045
Hello?

37:29.047 --> 37:31.881
Owen.
<i>Hey.</i>

37:31.883 --> 37:34.017
<i>How you feeling?</i>
<i>Okay.</i>

37:34.019 --> 37:36.119
Good. You're not calling me
from idaho, are you?

37:36.121 --> 37:37.354
No, I'm home.

37:37.356 --> 37:39.856
Good, stay there.

37:39.858 --> 37:42.225
Hey, can I ask you
a question?

37:42.227 --> 37:44.694
<i>Yeah, sure.</i>
<i>Go ahead.</i>

37:44.696 --> 37:47.797
If you delete something
from a hard drive,

37:47.799 --> 37:49.766
Is it gone forever?

37:49.768 --> 37:52.102
Because my--my dad
deleted something and--

37:52.104 --> 37:54.437
Well, they have those data
recovery programs,

37:54.439 --> 37:55.972
But if that doesn't work,

37:55.974 --> 37:58.074
You can always get a tech guy
to get it back.

37:58.076 --> 37:59.576
I might have a number
for you.

37:59.578 --> 38:01.211
No, thanks.
I'll let you know, though.

38:01.213 --> 38:02.379
<i>Okay.</i>

38:02.381 --> 38:04.147
Well, you rest up,
all right?

38:04.149 --> 38:06.883
I'll, uh, I'll
talk to you soon.

38:06.885 --> 38:08.385
<i>Bye.</i>
<i>Bye.</i>

38:14.925 --> 38:18.628
Why did you have
danny solano's skateboard?

38:20.965 --> 38:26.136
Why did you give danny solano's
skateboard to tom miller?

38:27.405 --> 38:29.773
What's your
favorite color?

38:29.775 --> 38:32.942
I want to see my dog.

38:32.944 --> 38:36.246
I'm not talking to you
till I see my dog.

38:36.248 --> 38:38.615
Oh, we're bargaining now,
are we?

38:38.617 --> 38:40.684
That's your choice.

38:43.120 --> 38:44.254
I see.

38:44.256 --> 38:47.123
Interview terminated
4:16 p.M.

38:47.125 --> 38:48.858
Think things over.

38:48.860 --> 38:51.594
I'm happy to keep you
locked up here all spring.

38:53.597 --> 38:55.332
Find her frigging dog.

38:55.334 --> 38:57.200
Now!

39:05.776 --> 39:08.845
[clattering]

39:23.961 --> 39:26.229
Tom?

39:34.872 --> 39:36.773
What are you doing?

39:39.810 --> 39:41.611
Nothing.

39:43.347 --> 39:44.914
Where's your mom
and dad?

39:44.916 --> 39:48.685
My mom's at work,
and my dad--

39:48.687 --> 39:50.587
He was putting
dylan to bed.

39:50.589 --> 39:53.390
I think
he fell asleep.

39:55.993 --> 39:58.495
Hmm.

40:08.506 --> 40:10.940
Is that your computer?

40:26.957 --> 40:28.591
What are we gonna do with you,
huh, boy?

40:28.593 --> 40:30.160
[dog whines]

40:55.319 --> 40:56.586
Are they still
on the line?

40:56.588 --> 40:58.154
No, they hung up.
I tried, but--

40:58.156 --> 41:00.723
Okay, all right.
Sir.

41:00.725 --> 41:02.225
Tell me you
found the dog.
No, sir--

41:02.227 --> 41:04.060
Find the dog.

41:04.062 --> 41:05.895
We can't do anything
till we find that bitch's dog.

41:05.897 --> 41:08.731
Sir, with respect,
shut up for a second.

41:08.733 --> 41:09.833
Did you just tell me
to shut up?

41:09.835 --> 41:11.267
Somebody just called.

41:11.269 --> 41:13.336
They saw a flashlight on
in the harvey ridge hut.

41:13.338 --> 41:15.505
The murder scene?
Haven't we sealed that off?

41:15.507 --> 41:17.740
Somebody's inside.

42:05.823 --> 42:07.223
[grunts]
ah!

42:10.060 --> 42:12.962
Come on!
Come on!

42:27.878 --> 42:30.246
Come out.

42:30.248 --> 42:31.814
Show yourself.

42:42.426 --> 42:45.495
[twig snaps, rustling]

42:47.831 --> 42:51.935
Carver?

42:51.937 --> 42:53.636
Sir?

42:56.774 --> 42:58.975
Is that you?

43:06.283 --> 43:08.017
[gunshot]

43:11.221 --> 43:13.957
[gasping]

43:15.192 --> 43:17.360
Sir.

43:17.362 --> 43:19.028
Go on!
Go on!

43:19.030 --> 43:21.397
Sir, what's happening?
What's happening?

43:21.399 --> 43:23.466
I think I'm dying.

43:23.468 --> 43:26.202
Oh, god.
Sir.

43:26.204 --> 43:28.972
[gasping and gagging]

43:28.974 --> 43:31.975
Okay, just breathe.
Breathe.

43:31.977 --> 43:33.543
Okay.
Okay.
